# Custom Banner with Theme Emojis and Borders
# String Alignment
ğŸ”§ 1. .center(width) - Centers the string in a field of given width.
ğŸ”§ 2. .ljust(width) - Left aligns the string and pads spaces to the right.
ğŸ”§ 3. .rjust(width) - Right aligns the string and pads spaces to the left.
ğŸ”§ 4. format() method with alignment specifiers: - Inside an f-string or str.format(), you can also control alignment:
Syntax	Meaning	Example
:<width>	Left align	
:>width	Right align	
:^width	Center align

